The “best” pet is far too vague a question.<P>The pet that puts out the most damage would probably be Magician.<P>That does not necessarily mean that they are the “best” all around pet though.<P>--------------------<P>Balance doesn&#8217;t always mean you getting more and/or others getting less. Sometimes you have to recognize that you should be the one to not get more, or to give something up.
