Best summoned pet - Magician's<P>Water pet, backstab, nuke<BR>Air pet, stun<BR>Earth pet, root<BR>Fire pet, damage shield, good nuke<P>Beast Lord's pets does more melee damage, and can tank well. But magicians have 4 pet types with different special abilities to choice from .<P>Dire Charmed pets from Enchanter of course has the best possible damage output.<P>--------------------<P>Hard decisions: Intel or AMD, Windows or Linux, Netscape or IE, Baldur's Gate II or Counter-Strike, computer or women.<BR>My Mains:<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=94174" TARGET=_blank>Xonic - 40 Bard</A>, <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87208" TARGET=_blank>Xinn - 46 Ranger</A>, <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=94182" TARGET=_blank>Xony - 32 Druid</A>
