<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Heres what I know:<P>Mages have the best pets.<P>Enchanters 55 pet, is a mage 34 pet, with higher damage, and less HP. <P>SK's have the worst pets.<P>Druids have the second worst pets.<P>Shaman pets do less damage than Enchanter pets, but are controlable.<P>Necros have the second best pets.<P>Beastlords are very close to Necros in the pet department, as far as I can tell, but you may want to get a more informed source on this point.<P>Cleric pets are very fun to watch.  I don't even know how to rate them.<P>--------------------<P>Dominus<BR>Mith Marr<BR>58 Enchanter<BR>---<BR>Are you scared?
