<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Couple of questions:<BR>1.	Why specifically a pet class?<BR>2.	Is the pet summoning class going to do anything at all besides send the pet in?<BR>3.	Does the pet need to be able to take hits as well as deliver damage?<BR>4.	Do you want highest pet damage or highest pet + summoning class damage?<BR>5.	What other classes are being played?<P>That’s a start. This is not as easily answered a question as you might believe.<P>--------------------<P>Balance doesn&#8217;t always mean you getting more and/or others getting less. Sometimes you have to recognize that you should be the one to not get more, or to give something up.
</FONT>
