<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I play five computers and I like both the necro and mage.  I started with a Druid/Necro combo then through in a enchanter then added a cleric then lastly a mage.  For those who wonder why a pet class it's pretty easy answer /pet attack in a hot key then play you other guys.  There is no way unless you want to start having seizures to play that many melees.  To get to your question though I think the necro has more utilities but mage is nice for putting down the mobs quicker and his pet will keep you alive more often then the necros until dire charm.  Not much help but I think they are pretty even the 58 necro spell Mind Wrack is awesome and necros are a very good class most people bashing them haven't played them to 60.  Good luck hope that helps a little.<P>--------------------<P>Venerable Kite 60 druid<BR>Hills 60 cleric<BR>Baroness Darjr 60 enchanter<BR>Sage Deadspout 60 necro<BR>Freye 60 magician<BR>Quellious<BR>Email: eqkite@yahoo.com
