<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Why don't you see more SK pets?<P>SK pets are different from every other class.  Pet is weaker than caster and has to be protected by caster.  A lot of people can't seem to figure that out.  SK is the tank not the Skeleton.<P>At low levels the SK pets are MUCH weaker.  Until you get to 49 pets aren't nearly as much help as other classes pets are.  Add to this the old pet rules and what you have is a level 42 SK casting a pet that aggros level 25 mobs.  A lot of people get tired of that fast and just stopped casting pets.<P>If SK is puller then having a pet is usually more trouble than it is worth.<P>This doesn't mean that they aren't worthwhile, just hard to play right -especially if you gave up on your pet at level 9.  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Onpur Spiritkin (Shaman)<BR>Armorer of the North<BR>Squigle Dmuerte (Shadow Knight)<BR>The Squigle of Death<BR>Basmac (Beastlord)
</FONT>
